                    <span>This book is all about the structure and flow of a story.  Nancy will show you how to hook the reader, how to dance through the crazy twists and turns that the reader will devour page after page, and how to leave them wanting to hand your book or story to a friend saying "you must read this!
<br />
<br />Mandatory for any author's bookshelf.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A great book on writing with clear and concise instructions</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
