                    <span>This is a great book due to the fact that it allows a novice (or experienced) writer an insight into the mechanics of storytelling.  There are exercises at the end of each chapter to enhance your novel or short story - which is very helpful in allowing a writer to look objectively at what he or she has written, to make the story well-written.<br>Recommendation: Buy it...</span>
                  
              
